# Mastermind member count

In the “Join the HTSA Mastermind Community” step, use **520+ members** for new invoices and frozen templates rebuilt via `scripts/build-htsa-invoice-templates.py`. (Legacy pages may still show older counts until updated.)

Example sentence:  
`Request access to the private Facebook Mastermind — where all live coaching call replays are posted and 520+ members support each other 24/7.`
